rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0001
rows.name: There—what is it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0002
rows.name: Lin?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0003
rows.name:
Incoming mobile target...
It's really, really big...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0004
rows.name: Bigger than caravan big![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0005
rows.name: Bigger than even legendary Frontier Village big![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0006
rows.name: If its transponders aren't responding to our IFF signal...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0007
rows.name: we have to assume it's hostile! Take cover![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0008
rows.name: Well well well, what do we have here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0009
rows.name:
A little appetizer of sorts before
we hit the city for the main course?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Wait—something that size, on that course...
It must be targeting NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0012
rows.name:
We can't let it get anywhere near the city.
We have to put a stop to it here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_JNK0010
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: xs10070100_SEL0011
rows.name: Swear to defeat it here.

rows.label: xs10070100_JNK0020
rows.name: Give Up

rows.label: xs10070100_SEL0021
rows.name: Abandon all hope and prepare to run.

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0013
rows.name:
I figured you'd say as much.
Remember, the entire city is counting on us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0014
rows.name: Let's knock this big piece of junk right outta the sky![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0015
rows.name: Run? Where you planning to go? We have to fight![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0016
rows.name: She's right. We have to protect the city. Let's go![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0017
rows.name: They stopped running...? They're even dumber than I thought![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0018
rows.name: Ryyz. Underestimating bad.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0019
rows.name: Yes, thanks for the brilliant insight there, genius.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10070100_MSG0020
rows.name:
Now sit back and watch while I
BURN THE HUMAN SCUM ALIVE![ST:wait ]
